thread.title: Shauna

author: Shauna
title: Shauna
text: Sent the Coppola Vineyard Taste of California Gift Basket for friends who were visiting California, staying at an AirBNB, and getting engaged. There were a lot of moving parts -- getting it delivered in time, signed for, and special enough for such a big occasion. Everything was perfect, and they were delighted with the basket and its contents. Best $80 bucks I ever spent.
